OL,3,C'Where are they?': Air India victims'
OL,4,Cfamily may have buried wrong remains
OL,6,FAltaf Taju lost his parents and
OL,7,Fbrother-in-law in the Air India flight
OL,8,Fwhich crashed on June 12, 2025, in
OL,9,FAhmedabad, India.
OL,11,FThe flight never arrived, and his
OL,12,Ffamily never came home.
OL,14,FParents Adam and Hasina Taju, along
OL,15,Fwith Taju's brother-in-law Altafhusen
OL,16,FPatel, were among the 241 people
OL,17,Fkilled on board. Only one passenger
OL,18,Fsurvived the crash.
OL,20,FFlight 171 was the worst aviation
OL,21,Fdisaster for the British since 9/11.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
