OL,3,C'Where are they?': Air India victims'
OL,4,Cfamily may have buried wrong remains
OL,6,F"We need answers. Where are they? My
OL,7,Funcle rings me on Sundays. He used to
OL,8,Fshow me the graves of my mum and
OL,9,Fdad... I've told him not to because I
OL,10,Fdon't know who I'm praying to."
OL,12,FOn a wintery day in London, we met
OL,13,FAltaf and his family.
OL,15,FAs we sat down for the interview,
OL,16,Fwhich lasted nearly an hour and a
OL,17,Fhalf, it became clear they were
OL,18,Fhaunted not just by the loss of their
OL,19,Floved ones but by the events
OL,20,Fsurrounding their deaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
