OL,3,C'Where are they?': Air India victims'
OL,4,Cfamily may have buried wrong remains
OL,6,F"We now sit at home and just pray to
OL,7,FGod that they rest in peace. We just
OL,8,Fleft everything to our God now because
OL,9,FI don't even look like the graves
OL,10,Fbecause I don't know who they are."
OL,12,FIt is a series of events that took
OL,13,Fplace in India and the UK that have
OL,14,Fled the family to question whether
OL,15,Fthey were given their loved ones to
OL,16,Fbury.
OL,18,FThe belongings that should have come
OL,19,Fhome with his parents instead appeared
OL,20,Fon social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
