OL,3,C'Where are they?': Air India victims'
OL,4,Cfamily may have buried wrong remains
OL,6,F"It was a male's tracksuit bottom...
OL,7,Fall burnt holes in it... in the
OL,8,Fpocket... it was a male's shaving
OL,9,Fcream tube," he said, describing the
OL,10,Fmoment he opened the container.
OL,12,F"My mother does not wear tracksuit
OL,13,Fbottoms."
OL,15,FThe room fell silent as he recounted
OL,16,Fwith a single tear that this was
OL,17,Fhanded over on the day of his mother's
OL,18,Fburial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
