OL,3,C'Where are they?': Air India victims'
OL,4,Cfamily may have buried wrong remains
OL,6,FAltaf told ITV News: "We bury in our
OL,7,Freligions, we have to bury where other
OL,8,Freligions cremate ... and thinking of
OL,9,Fwhat happened, where it could have
OL,10,Fbeen, don't want to say it, but my
OL,11,Fparents could have been cremated."
OL,13,FFor Altaf, the pain has been
OL,14,Fcompounded by a lack of answers and
OL,15,Faccountability.
OL,17,FHe is one of 40 British families who
OL,18,Fhave written to the Foreign Office
OL,19,Fasking for help.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
