OL,3,C'Where are they?': Air India victims'
OL,4,Cfamily may have buried wrong remains
OL,6,FA letter was sent in August, but
OL,7,Fthere's been no substantive reply.
OL,9,FWe asked Altaf whether anyone from the
OL,10,FBritish government had expressed their
OL,11,Fcondolences to him and his family.
OL,13,FWithout hesitation, he responded:
OL,14,F"Nothing. Nothing whatsoever."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
